{"tid":1920831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢一刻，我唔知點算好","createTime":"2020-03-11T17:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T04:22:45.000Z","uid":64769,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a8759779bc4ab5188dd8fdad6db70fcc10b91760","tid":1920831,"uid":64769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:02:17.000Z","msg":"我發覺社會真喺好現實，無論點發力去追都喺失敗<br />\n<br />\n幾年前，考DSE失敗左就搏左條命都要上返去大學<br />\n幾年後，結果上到啦又開始諗畢咗業之後點算好<br />\n到而家，仲有2個月左右就畢業同時間屋企人已經供緊樓<br />\n<br />\n每日一到夜晚頭都痛到爆，究竟要揾幾多物搞得掂<br />\n你話學業我死chur爛chur都捱到上去，但供樓我睇唔到希望<br />\n<br />\n身邊工作，又事事不順。幸好，有個女朋友陪伴住我，我先去到今時今日，<br />\n<br />\n而家既年青人真係好慘"},{"pid":"80d676623f45468bbe67ad4b3abb5c2984414cf8","tid":1920831,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T04:06:47.000Z","msg":"....... 以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45bcc0bcbba5c8a190af952801309eb7268f3b7","tid":1920831,"uid":23846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80d676623f45468bbe67ad4b3abb5c2984414cf8","tid":1920831,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T04:06:47.000Z","msg":"....... 以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"55"}]}